data.description: Welcome home!! 5216 Hurst Dr. is in a highly desired location in sought-after school zones. You walk right into a spacious living room, across from a formal dining room. Your kitchen overlooks your patio, ideal for entertaining and a tremendous yard perfect for all kinds of get-togethers. Going down the hallway you will see two ample sized guest bedrooms across from quite a substantial primary suite. In the already incredibly spacious garage you have tons of room for storage and ANOTHER heated/cooled room, previously used for home-schooling. Come see all this home has to offer & make it your own!
